Classical Nambu brackets  

There is a multi-linear, totally antisymmetric bracket, introduced by Nambu
.  On the full phase-space for a particle with  degrees of
freedom the highest rank, or maximal,  Nambu bracket (NB) is essentially
just the Jacobian
 
